text: Susana Canales Niaucel (5 September 1933 – 22 March 2021) was a Spanish actress. She starred in the 1951 drama Black Sky (1951).Bentley p.113 Canales died on 22 March 2021 in Madrid, at the age of 87.Muere la actriz Susana Canales, icono del cine de posguerra, a los 87 años ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1933 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Spanish movie actors Category:Spanish stage actors Category:Spanish television actors Category:Actors from Madrid
